However , <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Chen Pi - yun</ENAMEX> provided no reasonable explanation of the key question : Why were public funds mixed up with and deposited along with private funds in the <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Soong</ENAMEX> family 's private accounts ?
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Soong</ENAMEX> , who participated in <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Hsieh</ENAMEX> 's press conference , then declared that the mixing of public and private funds was done on the orders of party chairman <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Lee Teng - hui</ENAMEX> for purposes of " security , reliability , secrecy , and avoiding trouble . "
After the <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Hsieh - Chen - Soong</ENAMEX> press conference , the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">KMT</ENAMEX> held its own .
