<ENAMEX TYPE="EVENT">The Chung Hsing case</ENAMEX> may or may not be fully clarified , but it has certainly greatly affected <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">James Soong 's</ENAMEX> public support .
Before the scandal broke , he was getting more than <ENAMEX TYPE="PERCENT">30 %</ENAMEX> support in public opinion polls , but a <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">December 20</ENAMEX> poll by <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">the China Times</ENAMEX> shows <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Soong</ENAMEX> with only <ENAMEX TYPE="PERCENT">23 %</ENAMEX> .
